high_descs: Turn around and walk to the end of the white table to your right then turn left and walk to the coffee maker.
Get the dirty mug from under the coffee maker's spout.
Turn left and walk to the counter then move left until you're facing the spot between the microwave and sink.
Wash the mug off in the sink then pick it back up after you shut off the faucet.
Walk back to the coffee maker.
Put the mug back where you got it from.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug under the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the coffee maker.
Remove the cup from the coffee maker.
Turn to your left and approach the sink.
Place the cup in the sink, turn the faucet on and off and remove the cup.
Turn around and approach the coffee maker.
Place the cup in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean cup in the coffee maker.

high_descs: turn right to the coffee maker
wash the mug in the sink
turn around to the coffee maker
drop the mug on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: drop a clean mug on the coffee maker
